            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The <span class=\"iTxt\">Aqeeqa</span> regarding the boy and the girl, is the same’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "2. Abu Ali al-Ash‘ariy has narrated from Muhammad ‘Abd al-Jabbar and Muhammad ibn ’Isma‘il has narrated from al-Fadl ibn Shadhan from all Safwan from Mansur ibn Hazim who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘ ‘Aqiqah for boys and girls is the same.’” "
          ]
